                <ab>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī vijaiyābtam śālivāhana śakābtam 1448ṉ mēl cellā niṉṟa sarva vici samvatsarattu mēṣa nāyaṟṟu pūrva
<lb n="2"/>pakṣattu traiyōdaśiyum cani vāramum peṟṟa Uttirattu ṉāḷ coṉṉa vaṇṇam ceyta perumāḷ kōyilukku mēṟku kaṇṇan tāṅkal naṭātūr
<lb n="3"/>caratūta rācar putraṉ maṇṭalam veṭṭivitta kuḷakkaraiyil hanuma pratiṣṭaiyum paṇṇi kōyilu<unclear>m</unclear> maṇṭapamum kaṭṭivittu taṇṇīr pantalum vaippit
<lb n="4"/>hanumanta devaṟku naivēdya kaṭṭaḷai naṭakkumpaṭikku poliyūṭṭukku nāḷ Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭi Iru ṉāḻikku mā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Oṉṟukku tiru viḷakkukku Eṇ
<lb n="5"/>ṇai Iru nāḻikkum kuṭutta pa 25 Ip paṇam Irupattañcukkum cantrātittavaraiyum Inta Aruci Iru nāḻiyum Eṇṇai nāḻiyum hanumanta perumāḷukku nai
<lb n="6"/>ve<unclear>tya</unclear>m paṇṇi Itil <gap reason="lost" quantity="13" unit="character"/> lum taṇṇīr pantalum veṇ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>vaṉukku
